OL,3,CGrandad whose Christmas lights raised
OL,4,C#80K for charity retiring after 23
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FA man who has decorated his house with
OL,8,FChristmas lights for the last 23 years
OL,9,Ffor charity is officially 'retiring'
OL,10,Fthis year, making 2024 his last.
OL,12,FDerek Highe, near Huddersfield, has
OL,13,Fraised more than #80,000 through his
OL,14,Ffestive display which takes weeks to
OL,15,Finstall.
OL,17,FOn Sunday, 1 December, Mr Highe turned
OL,18,Fon the lights for the final time on
OL,19,Fhis street in Mirfield.
