OL,3,CGrandad whose Christmas lights raised
OL,4,C#80K for charity retiring after 23
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FMr Highe said: "We can't really
OL,8,Fbelieve when we started 23 years ago
OL,9,Fwhat we were going to start.
OL,11,FHe said that he had the idea to raise
OL,12,Fmoney through his illuminations
OL,13,Ffollowing the death of a close friend.
OL,15,F"Unfortunately a good friend of mine
OL,16,Frang me and said he had cancer but he
OL,17,Fwas going to be alright, but he passed
OL,18,Faway and I'd always put Christmas
OL,19,Flights up for my children," he said.
