OL,3,CGrandad whose Christmas lights raised
OL,4,C#80K for charity retiring after 23
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"I said to Joy my wife we might do
OL,8,Fsomething in his memory, never ever
OL,9,Frealising what we were starting."
OL,11,FThe display attracts hundreds of
OL,12,Ffamilies every year, including several
OL,13,Fwho travel from afar to see them.
OL,15,FHis daughter, Lucy Highe, said: "I see
OL,16,Ffirst hand the time and effort he puts
OL,17,Finto making a different theme each
OL,18,Fyear.
