OL,3,CGrandad whose Christmas lights raised
OL,4,C#80K for charity retiring after 23
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"I know Dad is extremely upset the
OL,8,Flights are coming to an end but as
OL,9,Fwe've said to him he's not getting any
OL,10,Fyounger and all good things must come
OL,11,Fto an end!"
OL,13,FThe Chief Executive of Kirkwood
OL,14,FHospice, Michael Crowther, said Mr
OL,15,FHighe has raised tens of thousands for
OL,16,Fthe hospice over the years.
OL,18,FMr Crowther said: "It's just
OL,19,Fincredible what Derek and his family
OL,20,Fhave done over the years.
